  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 36e87a4f269af074e86ec25091a07134, type: 3}
  m_Name: MadameLichenia_Intro
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueLines:
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: Madame... Lichenia?
  - Speaker: Madame Lichenia
    Text: "Zi-mi IMEDIAT de unde \u021Bi-ai luat cerceii!! Sunt *DIVINI*"
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: "\u0102\u0103\u0103 dintr-un t\xE2rg, cred"
  - Speaker: Madame Lichenia
    Text: "Excep\u021Bionali, merg excelent cu p\u0103rul t\u0103u. Pe roz nu aveau?"
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: "Parc\u0103 nu, erau singurul model"
  - Speaker: Madame Lichenia
    Text: Ce unfortunate!
  - Speaker: Madame Lichenia
    Text: "\u0218i e\u0219ti nou\u0103 prin \xEEmprejurimi, nu? Nu \xEE\u021Bi recunosc
      aura!"
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: Sunt, da
  - Speaker: Madame Lichenia
    Text: "Ai \xEEncercat ceva de la bar? Sunt cele mai bune b\u0103uturi din ora\u0219!"
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: "Nu, \xEEns\u0103 am auzit c\u0103 tu m\u0103 po\u021Bi ajuta \xEEn acest
      sens"
  - Speaker: Madame Lichenia
    Text: "Haha, drag\u0103! O s\u0103 devin\u0103 a usual \xEEn vocabularul t\u0103u
      expresia asta"
  choices:
  - choiceText: Care e treaba cu pansamentul gastric?
    nextDialogue: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ea9fb06605fb48e438797c58ffa596fe, type: 2}
